    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>“难道说……当我没有看向月亮时，月亮就不存在了吗？”</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《CASSETTE BOY / 卡带小子》是一款灵感源自量子力学的动作解谜RPG，玩家可以探索“未被观察之物便不存在”的神奇世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个景象会随视角切换而改变的世界中，揭开消失的月亮背后隐藏的谜团。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>看似2D，实则是3D的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乍看之下是怀旧的2D像素世界，实际上却是立体的3D空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过切换视角，收获全新的发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/b1e33370e6a5458ed09e1ba64a8a7c4e.poster.avif?t=1770888009\" width=1170 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/b1e33370e6a5458ed09e1ba64a8a7c4e.webm?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/b1e33370e6a5458ed09e1ba64a8a7c4e.mp4?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操控“所见之物”的解谜要素</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界里，看不见的事物便不存在。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过切换视角，将障碍物隐藏在视线之外以开辟道路，解开谜题，踏上冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/55df9791d84b2cd98725d0523cd8f94a.poster.avif?t=1770888009\" width=1170 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/55df9791d84b2cd98725d0523cd8f94a.webm?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/55df9791d84b2cd98725d0523cd8f94a.mp4?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动作要素与头目战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场冒险中，你将灵活运用旅途中获得的武器装备，挑战各类怪物与强大的头目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/fc7f9066237e01d5532fe36a98ee5004.poster.avif?t=1770888009\" width=1170 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/fc7f9066237e01d5532fe36a98ee5004.webm?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/fc7f9066237e01d5532fe36a98ee5004.mp4?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个性鲜明的登场角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个不可思议的世界中，你将邂逅众多个性鲜明的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与他们的相遇和对话，将让故事变得更加深刻且饱满。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/632836b094acd234fa73bc106e32c458.poster.avif?t=1770888009\" width=1170 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/632836b094acd234fa73bc106e32c458.webm?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/632836b094acd234fa73bc106e32c458.mp4?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集装备开启冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取多样的装备与武器，拓展探索与战斗的无限可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/90d2a299b4f734bed011f988d678e35b.poster.avif?t=1770888009\" width=1170 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/90d2a299b4f734bed011f988d678e35b.webm?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334330/extras/90d2a299b4f734bed011f988d678e35b.mp4?t=1770888009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 看不到的东西就不存在，独特的“视角”解谜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 通过旋转视角触发的各种机关</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 融合了解谜、探索与动作要素的游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 略带怀旧色彩，却又能带来新颖感受的解谜冒险游戏</p>",
